<link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../251/44251.xml">
Dakar</link></village>
. The film illustrates the poverty in Africa, showing that independence has not solved the problems of its people.<ref xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="#xpointer(//reflist/entry[@id=%221%22])">1</ref>
